{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- the-- the welcome was unlike it is nowadays today when you meet a friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everything was, like I mentioned, mixed with tears because our joy was-- was-- was to such a greater amount that you cannot show with laughing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to show it with crying somehow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever experienced in your life being happy and cry for happiness, but that's what it always showed in us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no end to tears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were coming right and left every time you met somebody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You say, oh, you survived, you survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "An impossible task which came true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I-- and I landed in Bratislava, where I met my friend from before who saw me on the street and came hugging me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I say, you saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You saved my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you dummy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were three years in Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was liberated in January.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look, you probably went through hell now for another four or five months, which I did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, that was meant to be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So little by little, I-- I made my way back from Bratislava, like I said, on trucks and this time already on Russian vehicles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and you know, a little food here, a little food there, until I came to Kosice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, what I'm telling you right now took a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't in a few days because bridges were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was all demolished and-- it was--.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But everything was-- was-- was happiness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, no matter what you endured now, there was-- it was all happiness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I come to Kosice, and I finally find a Russian soldier who said he'll take me to Michalovce.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's going there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
